{
  "texts": [
    "The inference was only applied to forest loss areas identified in 2.",
    "To estimate the number of samples needed for evaluating the map of forest loss drivers, we employed a stratified evaluation of area and accuracy based on 44.",
    "The number of samples and accuracy were calculated based on four lustra (2001-2005, 2006-2010, 2011-2015, and 2016-2020) in order to be able to assess temporal variations in the map accuracy and proportion of forest loss drivers.",
    "For each stratum (class), sample estimation weights were calculated based on the area estimation of each driver of forest loss for each time period.",
    "The calculated weights were utilized to determine the quantity of samples necessary to evaluate the map's accuracy for each driver over a five-year period."
  ]
}